PUBLIC Mode1, Mode2, Mode3
EXTRN DATA(modeNumber, delayDuration, temp)
EXTRN CODE (Delay, Init, Int0Handler, Int1Handler, T0Handler, T1Handler, SelectMode)
MAIN SEGMENT CODE
CSEG AT 0        
    JMP start
CSEG AT 0003H
	CALL Int0Handler
	JMP SelectMode
CSEG AT 0013H
	CALL Int1Handler
	JMP SelectMode
CSEG AT 000BH
	CALL T0Handler
	RET
CSEG AT 001BH
	CALL T1Handler
	RET  
USING 0
; Основная программа
RSEG MAIN
start:

CALL Init

MOV modeNumber, #3 ; Установка первого режима 

MOV delayDuration, #1 ; Установка длительности задержки 100 мс
CALL SelectMode

Mode1:
	MOV P1, #01010101B
	CALL Delay
	MOV A, P1
	RR A
	MOV P1, A
	CALL Delay
JMP Mode1

Mode2:
	MOV P1, #01010101B
	CALL Delay
	MOV A, P1
	RL A
	MOV P1, A
	CALL Delay
JMP Mode2

Mode3:
	MOV P1, #00001111B
	CALL Delay
	MOV A, P1
	SWAP A
	MOV P1, A
	CALL Delay
JMP Mode3
		
JMP start
END    





































































































































